ChangeList.Description: Added the **state** property to the [externalConnection](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/externalconnection?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the [externalGroup](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/externalgroup?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the [externalGroupMember](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/externalgroupmember?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Search more types in OneDrive and SharePoint: **drive**, **list**, **listItem**, and **site**. See [more details here](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/search-api-overview?view=graph-rest-beta&preserve-view=true#scope-search-based-on-entity-types).
Identify [selected properties](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/search-api-overview?view=graph-rest-beta&preserve-view=true#get-selected-properties) to return in search results.

[Sort](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/search-api-overview?view=graph-rest-beta&preserve-view=true#sort-search-results) search results from OneDrive and SharePoint by specifying **sortProperties** in a [searchRequest](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/searchRequest?view=graph-rest-beta&preserve-view=true) resource.

[Refine results using aggregations](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/search-api-overview?view=graph-rest-beta&preserve-view=true#refine-results-using-aggregations) for OneDrive and SharePoint by specifying **aggregations** and **aggregationFilters** in a **searchRequest** resource.
Query external data across [more than one connection](search-concept-custom-types.md).

Some properties in the request and response have been renamed and are deprecated.  See [more details](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/search-api-overview?view=graph-rest-beta&preserve-view=true#schema-change-deprecation-warning) about the deprecation.
Added the **aliases**, **isRefinable**, and **labels** properties to the [property](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/property?view=graph-rest-beta) entity.
Added the [get externalItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/externalitem-get?view=graph-rest-beta) operation.
The [externalFile](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/externalfile?view=graph-rest-beta) resource has been deprecated.
The [externalItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/externalfile?view=graph-rest-beta) resource now supports updating the **content** and **properties** properties.
Operations on [externalItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/externalfile?view=graph-rest-beta) resources now return a **Retry-After** header when they are throttled.

Added the [Microsoft Search API](search-concept-overview.md) that constitutes [querying](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/search-query?view=graph-rest-beta) and [indexing](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resource/indexing-api-overview?view=graph-rest-beta) capabilities.
Added the [query](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/search-query?view=graph-rest-beta) action.

Added the [searchRequest](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/searchrequest?view=graph-rest-beta), [searchQuery](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/searchquery?view=graph-rest-beta), [searchQueryString](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/searchquerystring?view=graph-rest-beta),[searchResponse](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/searchresponse?view=graph-rest-beta), [searchHitsContainer](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/searchhitscontainer?view=graph-rest-beta), and [searchHit](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/searchhit?view=graph-rest-beta) complex types.

Added the [externalConnection](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/externalconnection?view=graph-rest-beta), [schema](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/schema?view=graph-rest-beta), [externalItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/externalitem?view=graph-rest-beta), and [externalFile](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/externalfile?view=graph-rest-beta) entities, and methods exposed by these entities.
